{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01ScQBJrJLtJCYE4AXRBBBwm","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information needed. Let me construct the constraints.\n\n**Source Specs** (`docs/spec/auth.md`):\n\n**Session Management** (lines 3-5, section `#0002-session-management`):\n1. ログイン成功時、サーバーは HttpOnly かつ Secure な session cookie を発行する\n2. 通常の session 有効期限は 30 分\n\n\n3. logout 時には即時失効する\n\n**CSRF Protection** (lines 7-9, section `#0003-csrf-protection`):\n1. POST、PUT、PATCH、DELETE のように状態を変更する request は CSRF token を必須とする\n2. CSRF token が無い、または検証に失敗した request は 403 として拒否する\n\n**Core Concept** (`docs/core/concept.md`):\n- 認証は session cookie を中心に扱う。\n- CSRF 保護は state-changing request に必要である。\n\nNow I'm organizing the authentication constraints with their evidence sources. I need to document the session timeout, cookie security attributes, logout behavior, and CSRF token requirements for state-changing operations, each tied back to the specification documents.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":472,"cache_read_input_tokens":31776,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":472},"output_tokens":35,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2506604a-7ec0-4783-aad1-33400c75116f","uuid":"eccdcaa3-4442-4d7d-b6eb-4396232c6e9e","request_id":"req_011CbHr6rsXFEEzG63uNg6af"}
